title: Proposal for a BunnyPark Syrup Pool and Farm
body:
# PancakeSwap Welcomes BunnyPark to Syrup Pool!


CAKE holders, today we are happy to be able to offer you a new Syrup Pool from BunnyPark, a  DeFi + NFT project deployed on BSC focusing on NFT SaaSization.




# The Syrup Pool:
Stake CAKE tokens to earn BP tokens!

- **Total Tokens:** 375,000 BP 
- **Distribution duration:** 60 days
- **Start block:** 10560250 [**(approx. 9am UTC on September 2nd)**](https://www.bscscan.com/block/countdown/10560250)
- **Finish block:** 12288250 [**(approx. 9am UTC on November 1st)**](https://www.bscscan.com/block/countdown/12288250)
- **Token rewards per block:** 0.217 BP


## Max Stake per wallet: 
100 CAKE for the first 48 hours, then unlimited CAKE staking afterwards. 

To give as many CAKE holders the opportunity to Farm some juicy pool rewards at a high APY, we will have a 100 CAKE token cap staking limit per user for the first 48 hours.


# The Farm:
In order to host the BP Syrup Pool, we will need to provide a BP-BNB farm that will have 1x CAKE rewards for the first 48 hours and then 0.5x CAKE rewards after that. 


# What is BunnyPark?
BunnyPark is a DeFi + NFT project deployed on BSC focusing on NFT SaaSization and product standardization that allows the output of NFT development standards, diverse gameplay, product rules and application values into a series of standard smart contracts. Being the Lego provider in the NFT sector, provides many NFT and GameFi developer teams and artists quick combinations to create NFT product platforms.
 
BunnyPark owns an independent "SaaS" incubation fund. We are always open to accepting applications from  development teams and artists. The successful teams who pass our review will receive fundings, R&D, mathematical models, operations and other comprehensive support provided by the incubation fund.






### To learn more about BunnyPark, the chefs advise you to visit their official communication channels:

- **Website:** [https://www.bunnypark.com/](https://www.bunnypark.com/)
- **Twitter:** [https://twitter.com/bunnypark_bsc](https://twitter.com/bunnypark_bsc)
- **Telegram:** [https://t.me/bunnyparkbsc01](https://t.me/bunnyparkbsc01)	
- **Medium:** [https://bunnyparkbsc.medium.com/](https://bunnyparkbsc.medium.com/)	


# How do you stake CAKE to earn BP rewards?
If you own CAKE tokens, congratulations! You’re the master of your … pancakes.
Time to step up your taste buds by learning how to stake CAKE with Syrup Pool.
- Visit this webpage: [**https://pancakeswap.finance/syrup** ](https://pancakeswap.finance/syrup )
- Click “Approve CAKE” on the BP Syrup Pool 
- Click on the stake button.
- Confirm the transaction.

BEP20 BP will also be circulating and transferable on BSC when we start the Syrup pool, so you will be able to harvest your BP tokens and trade on PancakeSwap at any time!



# BEWARE OF FOOD POISONING! ⚠️⚠️⚠️💀

The official BP token contract address on Binance Smart Chain is:
[**https://www.bscscan.com/token/0xacb8f52dc63bb752a51186d1c55868adbffee9c1**](https://www.bscscan.com/token/0xacb8f52dc63bb752a51186d1c55868adbffee9c1)

Any other BP token will be a scam and will result in a financial loss for users. Do not buy tokens from any other token address. Always verify the token address before purchasing tokens. If you receive airdrops from another address for BP tokens, they will be rotten tokens (but not the cool kind!), and we advise you to ignore them.
